data.description: *OPEN HOUSE* October 1, 2023 from 1-3PM - If you've been searching for that farm house charm with all of the modern amenities of a new home well, look no further! This is the home for YOU! Built in 1900 with the Historic character you'd expect, this homestead has been renovated and upgraded THROUGHOUT! The Location ALSO gives you the best of the country life and suburban life! Seated just minutes from shopping, restaurants, and the Hospital campus off Dupont, and the new Vinland Winery. The 2.5+ acre not too big not too small property goes perfectly with the country yet suburban feel with 3 outbuildings! A 40x30 double level Historic barn that has been recently UPGRADED as well! Featuring new insulation, newer fireplace heat, 100 Amp electric, new Metal roof w/ transferable LIFETIME Warranty, custom built barn doors and newly built loft w/ double wide staircase leading up! A newer 20x12 shed w/ oversized barn doors new metal roof and electrical added! Within a few steps from the home is an INSULATED, epoxied floor, Air Conditioned, with electric, 3 car garage! The home is BEAUTIFUL with yesteryear charm galore! Featuring 5 Bedrooms, 2 FULL baths , 1 Half Baths, 3,700+/- sqft, 2 FULL Kitchens w/ R/O water systems, CUSTOM hardwood cabinets and countertops, all NEWER Appliances, window treatments, and security system w/ cameras included! Have someone you'd like to ave live with you but require their own space? PERFECT! There is an an ADA accessible in-law suite/apartment with FULL Kitchen, Bedroom, and FULL Bathroom! You'll have peace of mind with the MAJOR Upgrades & Updates throughout including both kitchens, bathrooms, NEWER ROOF, Windows, Floor coverings, added french drain system around the home and property, DRY basement great for storage, home is connected to SEWER and on your own well for water!  Your property will be where ALL of your friends and family will want to be! Imagine them playing basketball on your own private FULL sized basketball court with 2 Goalrilla goals/tennis court with nets included and they'll be sure to LOVE the CUSTOM in-ground CEMENT pool with waterfall connections and custom painted cement 80x21 cement back patio! Truly is so much to see and appreciate here that this. Is. A. MUST. SEE!
